 R←Test_SmartTypo_001(stopFlag batchFlag);⎕TRAP;ns;html;md;two;parms
⍝ Test how a single double quote is dealt with.
 ⎕TRAP←(999 'C' '. ⍝ Deliberate error')(0 'N')
 R←∆Failed

 md←''
 md,←⊂'Header "one'
 md,←⊂'===='
 md,←⊂''
 md,←⊂'## Header "two'
 md,←⊂''
 md,←⊂'1. First is odd"'
 md,←⊂'1. Second'
 md,←⊂''
 md,←⊂'* This is "odd'
 md,←⊂'* That'
 md,←⊂''
 md,←⊂'> This "is a blockquote'
 md,←⊂''
 md,←⊂'An ordinary para".'
 md,←⊂''
 md,←⊂'This para "stretches over two lines,'
 md,←⊂'but in total the number of " is even, not odd!'
 md,←⊂''
 md,←⊂'|Col 1"|Col 2|'
 md,←⊂'|-|-|'
 md,←⊂'|"First|Second|'
 md,←⊂''
 md,←⊂'|"A1|B1|'
 md,←⊂'|"A2|B2|'
 md,←⊂''

 parms←##.MarkAPL.CreateParms
 parms.verbose←0
 ns←##.MarkAPL.Init parms md
 ns←##.MarkAPL.Process ns

 html←1↓⊃,/(⎕UCS 13),¨ns.html
 →PassesIf 1=+/'Header "one'⍷html
 →PassesIf 1=+/'Header "two'⍷html
 →PassesIf 1=+/'First is odd"'⍷html
 →PassesIf 1=+/'This is "odd'⍷html
 →PassesIf 1=+/'This "is a blockquote'⍷html
 →PassesIf 1=+/'An ordinary para".'⍷html
 →PassesIf 1=+/'“'⍷html
 →PassesIf 1=+/'”'⍷html
 →PassesIf 1=+/'Col 1"'⍷html
 →PassesIf 1=+/'"First'⍷html
 →PassesIf 1=+/'"A1'⍷html
 →PassesIf 1=+/'"A2'⍷html
 →PassesIf 10=⊃⍴ns.report

 R←∆OK
